{"tid":691221,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"見工問題一問","createTime":"2018-06-05T13:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T16:52:29.000Z","uid":8054,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28ff2c09d81282e6d2c998adc7376ad69aabb77b","tid":691221,"uid":8054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小妹五月中個陣in 左一份中學TA<br />\n間中學已經口頭上比左offer 我<br />\n但由於個陣學校仲係考緊試<br />\n咁學校個邊就話要等我出埋成績證明我真係修滿學分畢到業先會準備約比我簽<br />\n我最近出左成績無fail 成功畢業<br />\n咁我就第一時間印份transcript 比佢<br />\n之後遞個陣我問校務處d 職員 問佢幾時會簽約<br />\n跟住個職員就話：<br />\n「因為有另一個人都要準備合約<br />\n校長想等埋佢交d 文件再準備份約<br />\n有消息再通知你」<br />\n我一聽到佢咁講就好不安<br />\n我唔知佢地係真係請左唔止一個ta<br />\n定係想拎我份成績同第二個人比較再決定簽唔簽我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申，我cgpa 3.09 叫做啱啱好sec up 到<br />\n四年黎有fail 過一科<br />\n張成績表唔算好靚<br />\n如果真係同人比 我驚比唔上<br />\n（但個校長應該係滿意我面試表現的）<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家<br />\n我依加呢個情況姐係點? <br />\n佢會唔會請我？<br />\n呢兩日我個心成日lor lor 亂<br />\n求各位巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪擔心啦佢準備緊份約姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以收皮搵過第二份"},{"pid":"4bd7f71f9702389e639c97d99f9841cb9c8ce109","tid":691221,"uid":8054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebba6100e6e4937a000cb819232b8e556af3c11","tid":691221,"uid":8054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:49:45.000Z","msg